---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Asia Pacific | ARM Management"
  description="ARM Management advises on company formation, accounting, payroll, global mobility, and transaction advisory across Singapore, Hong Kong, Malaysia, India, Vietnam, Thailand, Indonesia, and Japan."
>
<main>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__bg" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1525625293386-3f8f99389edd?w=1600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__content container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Asia Pacific</span>
      <h1>Asia Pacific</h1>
      <p>Singapore, Hong Kong, Malaysia, India, Vietnam, Thailand, Indonesia, and Japan.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Overview</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">ARM Management in Asia Pacific</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal">Asia Pacific represents some of the world's most dynamic and commercially significant markets. Singapore and Hong Kong serve as the region's primary entry points for international businesses — offering common law legal systems, strong financial infrastructure, and favourable tax regimes. ARM Management advises clients expanding into these and the wider APAC region from initial market assessment through to ongoing compliance.</p>
      <p class="reveal" style="margin-top:20px">Beyond Singapore and Hong Kong, the region presents significant complexity: Vietnam's foreign investment approval processes, India's FDI restrictions and regulatory layering, Indonesia's local ownership requirements, and Japan's language and administrative barriers. ARM Management navigates these environments on behalf of clients, coordinating vetted local professionals through a single senior relationship.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--warm" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal">Services in Asia Pacific</span>
      <h2 class="reveal">What ARM Management Does Here</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal" style="color:#6B7280;margin-bottom:40px">All six ARM practice areas are available across Asia Pacific. Click any service to learn more.</p>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <a href="/services/transaction-advisory" class="card reveal reveal-delay-1" style="text-decoration:none;display:block">
          <h3>Transaction Advisory</h3>
          <p>Cross-border investment and M&amp;A advisory across Singapore, Hong Kong, Malaysia, India, and the wider APAC region.</p>
          <span class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top:8px;display:inline-block">Learn More →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/company-formation" class="card reveal reveal-delay-2" style="text-decoration:none;display:block">
          <h3>Company Formation</h3>
          <p>Private limited companies and branch offices in Singapore, Hong Kong, Malaysia, India, Vietnam, Thailand, Indonesia, and Japan.</p>
          <span class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top:8px;display:inline-block">Learn More →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/accounting-tax" class="card reveal reveal-delay-3" style="text-decoration:none;display:block">
          <h3>Accounting &amp; Tax</h3>
          <p>Coordinated accounting and tax compliance across APAC jurisdictions, including Singapore GST and corporate tax.</p>
          <span class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top:8px;display:inline-block">Learn More →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/payroll-hr" class="card reveal reveal-delay-1" style="text-decoration:none;display:block">
          <h3>Payroll &amp; HR</h3>
          <p>Multi-country payroll compliance and employment advisory across Singapore, Hong Kong, and other APAC markets.</p>
          <span class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top:8px;display:inline-block">Learn More →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/global-mobility" class="card reveal reveal-delay-2" style="text-decoration:none;display:block">
          <h3>Global Mobility</h3>
          <p>Singapore EntrePass, Employment Pass, and investor visa advisory. Hong Kong residency and talent visa programmes.</p>
          <span class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top:8px;display:inline-block">Learn More →</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/crypto-web3" class="card reveal reveal-delay-3" style="text-decoration:none;display:block">
          <h3>Crypto &amp; Web3</h3>
          <p>MAS regulatory advisory for Singapore. SFC licensing guidance for Hong Kong virtual asset service providers.</p>
          <span class="btn-secondary" style="margin-top:8px;display:inline-block">Learn More →</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--navy">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow reveal" style="color:#B8960C">Key Jurisdictions</span>
      <h2 class="reveal" style="color:#F7F3EC">Where We Operate</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <div style="margin-top:40px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:24px">
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="padding:24px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.2);border-radius:2px">
          <h4 style="color:#B8960C;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:10px">Singapore</h4>
          <p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:14px;line-height:1.75">Private limited companies, GST, corporate tax, CPF payroll, EntrePass and Employment Pass. MAS regulatory advisory for financial services and VASPs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="padding:24px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.2);border-radius:2px">
          <h4 style="color:#B8960C;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:10px">Hong Kong</h4>
          <p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:14px;line-height:1.75">Limited company formation, profits tax, MPF payroll, VASP licensing under SFC. One of Asia's leading financial and crypto regulatory centres.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1" style="padding:24px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.2);border-radius:2px">
          <h4 style="color:#B8960C;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:10px">Malaysia, India &amp; Thailand</h4>
          <p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:14px;line-height:1.75">Sdn Bhd and branch formation in Malaysia. Private limited company formation in India with FDI compliance. BOI-promoted entities in Thailand.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2" style="padding:24px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1px solid rgba(184,150,12,.2);border-radius:2px">
          <h4 style="color:#B8960C;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:10px">Vietnam, Indonesia &amp; Japan</h4>
          <p style="color:rgba(247,243,236,.65);font-size:14px;line-height:1.75">Foreign investment advisory and LLC formation in Vietnam. PT PMA structures in Indonesia. KK and GK formation in Japan.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2 class="reveal">Begin Your Asia Pacific Expansion</h2>
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Speak with a senior ARM advisor about your requirements in Asia Pacific. We will give you an honest assessment of what is achievable, on what timeline, and at what cost.</p>
    <div class="btn-row reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
</Base>
